{"tid":2299821,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"不敵《鬼滅之刃》新海誠感氣餒","createTime":"2020-11-25T04:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T04:57:27.000Z","uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29588b0387546944af6805c8666a103a8db7f23d","tid":2299821,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】日本勞動節長假結束，動畫電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》票房報捷，截至前日為止，上映39日累計票房達259億日圓（約19.1億港元），超越《你的名字》和《魔雪奇緣》紀錄，成為日本史上最賣座電影第3位，相信短期內亦將打破《鐵達尼號》保持多年不敗的262億日圓佳績，取而代之成為最賣座電影亞軍，並挑戰另一動畫大師宮崎駿的《千與千尋》冠軍位置（308億日圓）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《你的名字》導演新海誠昨日透過社交媒體回應：「咦？已經！？笑。雖然感到氣餒，但紀錄是用來打破的，我會竭盡所能，繼續製作好電影。」粉絲紛紛留言為他打氣，並期待《天氣之子》後的新作盡快面世。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%a8%9b%e6%a8%82/article/20201125/s00016/1606242054624/%e4%b8%8d%e6%95%b5%e3%80%8a%e9%ac%bc%e6%bb%85%e4%b9%8b%e5%88%83%e3%80%8b%e6%96%b0%e6%b5%b7%e8%aa%a0%e6%84%9f%e6%b0%a3%e9%a4%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%25a8%259b%25e6%25a8%2582%2Farticle%2F20201125%2Fs00016%2F1606242054624%2F%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2595%25b5%25e3%2580%258a%25e9%25ac%25bc%25e6%25bb%2585%25e4%25b9%258b%25e5%2588%2583%25e3%2580%258b%25e6%2596%25b0%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e8%25aa%25a0%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%25b0%25a3%25e9%25a4%2592&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKIleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c3a1f899\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%25a8%259b%25e6%25a8%2582%2Farticle%2F20201125%2Fs00016%2F1606242054624%2F%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%2595%25b5%25e3%2580%258a%25e9%25ac%25bc%25e6%25bb%2585%25e4%25b9%258b%25e5%2588%2583%25e3%2580%258b%25e6%2596%25b0%